BT /F1 12 Tf 54 738 Td (accidental sharing of tokens.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 718 Td (JWTs should contain only the minimum information needed for authentication and) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 702 Td (authorization. For this project, the token should include the username, role, expiry) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 686 Td (time, issued-at time, and token ID. This follows the principle of least privilege by) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 670 Td (limiting the token to only the claims required by the backend.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 650 Td (Recommended JWT payload:) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 68 628 Td ({) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 68 612 Td (  "sub": "alice",) Tj ET
