BT /F1 12 Tf 64 426 Td (- Standard users can access only their profile.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 64 410 Td (- Admin users can access profile data and delete users.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 64 394 Td (- Admin-only routes must verify the role claim and must not rely on hidden frontend) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 78 378 Td (controls.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 64 362 Td (- Unauthorized admin-route attempts should return 403 Forbidden and be logged to) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 78 346 Td (security.log.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 330 Td (This prevents a standard user from guessing admin URLs or forcing access to) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 54 314 Td (privileged backend actions.) Tj ET
